name: Help Japan Poster
description:
Help Raise money for Japan by buying this Vector Illustration poster. Your  £3 goes to the  people in japan. So please show support and buy your poster today.. Plus you do get the Rather cute Japaneses sun. 

Printed on A3 Gloss paper.

So Do your part and Donate now!

-----------------------------------------

P&P 

UK - £1
Rest of the world - £1.50

These prices cover shipping, and the poster tube its sent in
